name: Movement Report
query:
SELECT
`tabStock Entry`.`name` as "ID:Link/Stock Entry:100",
`tabStock Entry`.`posting_date` as "Posting Date:Date:100",
`tabStock Entry`.`company` as "Company::200",
`tabStock Entry Detail`.`item_code` as "Item Code::120",
`tabStock Entry Detail`.`item_name` as "Item Name::250",
`tabStock Entry Detail`.`item_group` as "Item Group::100",
`tabStock Entry Detail`.`country` as "Country::80",
`tabStock Entry Detail`.`s_warehouse` as "Source Wareshouse::150",
`tabStock Entry Detail`.`t_warehouse` as "Target Wareshouse::150",
`tabStock Entry Detail`.`qty` as "Qty::80",
`tabStock Entry Detail`.`basic_rate` as "Rate::80",
`tabStock Entry Detail`.`basic_amount` as "Amount::100",
`tabStock Entry Detail`.`valuation_rate` as "Valuation Rate::100"
FROM
`tabStock Entry`
Left Join `tabStock Entry Detail` ON `tabStock Entry`.name =`tabStock Entry Detail`.parent
WHERE
`tabStock Entry`.stock_entry_type = 'Material Transfer'
